WEBVTT

00:12.720 --> 00:14.480
Didn't you want to be Queen Chu?

00:15.080 --> 00:17.480
Haven't you always wanted to replace her?

00:18.390 --> 00:19.850
I'm giving you the chance.

00:22.280 --> 00:24.000
Why aren't you taking it?

00:26.510 --> 00:27.030
I...

00:28.120 --> 00:29.030
didn't...

00:38.310 --> 00:39.110
Your Majesty,

00:39.670 --> 00:42.240
I have nothing but admiration for the bond
between you and Queen Chu,

00:42.240 --> 00:43.640
and no trace of jealousy.

00:44.430 --> 00:45.670
If my death

00:46.000 --> 00:48.280
could make Queen Chu
change her mind and return to you,

00:48.280 --> 00:50.680
I would willingly die before you
right now.

00:51.670 --> 00:53.390
You won't die like this.

00:53.640 --> 00:55.000
Let me tell you...

00:56.030 --> 00:57.240
where to stab...

00:59.000 --> 01:00.640
to kill yourself.

01:14.640 --> 01:15.280
Leave!

01:58.340 --> 01:59.289
My Lady.

02:09.120 --> 02:10.050
You are injured?

02:11.080 --> 02:12.430
I'll go get you some medicine.

02:12.430 --> 02:13.290
Leave me alone.

02:14.240 --> 02:15.370
I didn't betray you.

02:16.400 --> 02:18.400
You don't need to pretend to be kind.

02:18.840 --> 02:20.120
Since I agreed to cooperate with you,

02:20.120 --> 02:21.430
I will keep my promise.

02:22.280 --> 02:23.430
You can go back now.

02:24.150 --> 02:25.610
Since it's a cooperation,

02:25.840 --> 02:27.590
it means we share the same goal.

02:28.079 --> 02:29.940
You are not just doing this for me,

02:30.250 --> 02:32.910
but also to fulfill your role
as Consort Helian.

02:33.150 --> 02:34.810
You chose this path yourself.

02:35.110 --> 02:37.000
From the beginning, you should have known

02:37.000 --> 02:38.329
that life around Yan Xun

02:39.540 --> 02:40.200
is not easy.

02:47.630 --> 02:49.630
If I hadn't become Consort Helian,

02:51.680 --> 02:53.050
I would already have been

02:53.050 --> 02:56.079
the fourth concubine
of Elder Tubu of Hongchuan Tribe.

02:56.079 --> 02:57.910
I am a daughter of the Helian family.

02:57.910 --> 03:00.470
Helian Tribe is the smallest
among the Great Yan tribes.

03:00.470 --> 03:02.360
This is a fate I cannot change.

03:02.880 --> 03:04.080
Ever since I was born,

03:04.630 --> 03:07.040
I knew that all the tribal elders
of Great Yan

03:07.040 --> 03:09.960
had their eyes on us,

03:10.850 --> 03:13.850
always wanting to divide
and swallow Helian Tribe.

03:16.740 --> 03:18.090
And my brother...

03:20.310 --> 03:22.829
He never once stopped waiting for me
to grow up,

03:22.829 --> 03:23.960
thinking of using me

03:24.430 --> 03:25.310
in exchange for

03:25.310 --> 03:27.470
a few horses and grazing lands.

03:30.280 --> 03:32.430
Do you think I had any better choice

03:32.430 --> 03:34.520
than becoming Consort Helian?

03:36.000 --> 03:37.430
Even my maids know

03:38.030 --> 03:40.760
Yan Xun has never truly spent the night
in my room.

03:41.360 --> 03:42.620
You think I don't know?

03:42.750 --> 03:44.400
He just wanted to silence the gossip

03:44.400 --> 03:45.190
by giving me this

03:45.190 --> 03:46.920
pitiful and ridiculous title.

04:03.430 --> 04:04.490
What are you doing?

04:06.380 --> 04:07.190
Don't move.

04:08.110 --> 04:09.310
Your foot is injured.

04:10.480 --> 04:11.610
I'll carry you back.

05:42.409 --> 05:47.650
[REBIRTH]

05:48.130 --> 05:50.770
[Episode 19]

05:52.630 --> 05:53.390
Yan Qing,

05:53.870 --> 05:56.980
is there any news from the person
we sent to Zhan's Mansion yesterday?

05:56.980 --> 05:57.780
Your Majesty,

05:57.920 --> 05:58.720
not yet.

05:59.430 --> 06:01.760
But he is still waiting at Zhan's Mansion.

06:01.890 --> 06:03.730
He said that as soon as there's news
about Lord Zhan,

06:03.730 --> 06:05.370
he will come to the palace to report.

06:05.370 --> 06:06.490
He went yesterday.

06:07.070 --> 06:08.920
Why is there still no news?

06:09.420 --> 06:10.880
Don't worry, Your Majesty.

06:10.880 --> 06:12.650
Today is the 15th.

06:12.830 --> 06:14.560
His Majesty has been ill for a long time.

06:14.560 --> 06:16.340
The officials are all at Xiangtian Hall,

06:16.340 --> 06:18.540
waiting for you to pray for His Majesty.

06:46.340 --> 06:48.540
Recently, His Majesty has been unwell.

06:49.280 --> 06:52.720
I will personally pray to the ancestors

06:52.920 --> 06:54.720
to bless him.

06:54.750 --> 06:56.610
Xiangtian Hall is a sacred place.

06:56.700 --> 06:58.780
You should not disturb it.

06:59.230 --> 07:00.630
Yes, Your Majesty.

07:06.080 --> 07:07.370
Ancestors above,

07:08.010 --> 07:11.220
may you bless Biantang with peace

07:11.250 --> 07:13.040
and stability for generations,

07:13.040 --> 07:16.100
and may our Emperor receive the protection
of his forebears,

07:16.100 --> 07:18.100
enjoying long life and good health.

08:07.620 --> 08:08.370
Nobody move!

08:13.070 --> 08:14.190
It's you.

08:14.750 --> 08:16.150
What exactly do you want?

08:16.260 --> 08:18.530
Why do you have Zhan Ziyu's jade pendant?

08:18.700 --> 08:20.050
Zhan Ziyu is dead.

08:21.300 --> 08:22.900
I want to make a deal with you.

08:23.360 --> 08:24.400
You let Li Ce go,

08:24.800 --> 08:26.330
and I will keep your secret.

08:26.560 --> 08:28.020
Let's each take a step back

08:28.270 --> 08:29.930
and leave each other a way out.

08:30.270 --> 08:32.320
Why would I need a way out?

08:32.610 --> 08:34.610
Zhan Ziyu's identity is not simple.

08:34.990 --> 08:37.429
Back then, when the Biantang Emperor
carried out a purge of the Nanxi Tribe,

08:37.429 --> 08:39.559
Zhan Ziyu survived by a stroke of luck.

08:39.590 --> 08:40.860
You took him in

08:41.390 --> 08:44.650
and used him to train the Nanxi people
as suicide warriors.

08:45.110 --> 08:48.270
The assassination attempt in Qinzheng Hall
on His Majesty that day

08:48.270 --> 08:49.790
was your order.

08:49.870 --> 08:50.630
Yesterday,

08:51.200 --> 08:53.600
Zhan Ziyu attempted
to assassinate the Crown Prince

08:53.600 --> 08:54.800
on his way to Youzhou.

08:54.840 --> 08:56.200
It was also your order.

08:59.240 --> 09:00.150
Your Majesty,

09:00.910 --> 09:03.510
even though the Biantang Emperor
has favored you for many years,

09:03.510 --> 09:05.390
Li Ce is his only bloodline

09:05.790 --> 09:07.450
and the sole heir of Biantang.

09:07.550 --> 09:09.510
Why did you attempt
regicide and rebellion?

09:09.510 --> 09:10.900
Once His Majesty recovers,

09:10.900 --> 09:12.870
he will eventually realize the truth.

09:12.870 --> 09:13.670
So it's better

09:14.440 --> 09:16.550
to pin all the blame on Lord Zhan

09:16.630 --> 09:18.960
before he wakes up to it,

09:19.480 --> 09:22.750
so that neither you nor the Crown Prince
will be implicated.

09:22.750 --> 09:25.270
Your Majesty, if you are willing to clear
the Crown Prince's name,

09:25.270 --> 09:27.820
I am willing to leave the Crown Prince
from this moment on

09:27.820 --> 09:29.280
and take Lord Zhan's place

09:29.940 --> 09:31.220
to work for you.

09:34.360 --> 09:37.840
Raising assassins,
attempting to kill His Majesty,

09:38.440 --> 09:39.960
and framing the Crown Prince?

09:39.960 --> 09:41.490
What are you talking about?

09:42.020 --> 09:43.620
I don't understand at all.

09:44.190 --> 09:47.190
The Nanxi Tribe was wiped out long ago.

09:48.270 --> 09:51.440
Their village back then

09:51.910 --> 09:55.270
was burned to the ground years ago.

09:55.800 --> 09:58.880
The Nanxi people have lived by the water
for generations.

09:58.880 --> 10:01.480
How could fire alone wipe them out
completely?

10:02.340 --> 10:04.800
The wooden houses they lived in
for generations

10:04.800 --> 10:07.150
were located in a valley
backed by the South Mountain.

10:07.150 --> 10:08.960
If the fire was set

10:09.670 --> 10:10.960
in a specific season

10:11.510 --> 10:12.640
and at a specific location,

10:12.640 --> 10:14.410
none of them could escape.

10:15.420 --> 10:17.480
Your Majesty,
how do you know this so clearly?

10:17.480 --> 10:20.280
The secret imperial order
given to Sun Di back then

10:20.910 --> 10:22.200
was issued by you

10:22.580 --> 10:23.980
personally.

10:26.660 --> 10:28.140
You've said so much.

10:28.970 --> 10:30.230
What proof do you have?

10:48.440 --> 10:49.240
Impossible.

10:49.970 --> 10:52.600
The order to annihilate the Nanxi Tribe
was issued by Biantang Emperor.

10:52.600 --> 10:54.660
It had nothing to do with Her Majesty.

10:55.060 --> 10:56.390
You're just saying this

10:56.550 --> 10:58.680
to make me testify against Her Majesty

10:58.930 --> 11:01.190
and admit that it was her
who sent me here.

11:01.720 --> 11:03.010
No matter what you say,

11:03.030 --> 11:04.270
I won't betray her.

11:04.730 --> 11:06.220
Even if you kill me,

11:06.680 --> 11:09.750
I won't say a word against her!

11:10.270 --> 11:11.000
Back then,

11:11.790 --> 11:14.760
Biantang Emperor sent troops
to wipe out the Nanxi village.

11:14.760 --> 11:16.490
But after several deployments,

11:16.490 --> 11:19.020
they still couldn't
defeat them completely.

11:19.030 --> 11:21.490
The Empress,
in order to please her husband,

11:22.220 --> 11:23.460
went to great lengths

11:23.930 --> 11:24.800
and finally found a way

11:24.800 --> 11:26.870
to wipe out the Nanxi Tribe

11:27.000 --> 11:28.550
by exploiting the unique structure

11:28.550 --> 11:30.390
and terrain of their settlements

11:30.390 --> 11:32.250
to set the entire village on fire.

11:43.200 --> 11:43.870
Zhen,

11:44.790 --> 11:46.750
tell me this isn't true.

11:47.320 --> 11:48.960
This isn't true.

12:00.630 --> 12:01.280
Run!

12:05.120 --> 12:05.750
Ziming!

12:06.030 --> 12:06.670
Ziming!

12:18.870 --> 12:19.480
Don't run!

12:22.870 --> 12:23.480
Stop!

12:31.280 --> 12:32.540
A remnant of the Nanxi Tribe?

12:32.540 --> 12:34.340
How dare you offend the Empress?

12:35.130 --> 12:35.730
Step back.

12:57.360 --> 12:58.390
This is for you.

13:05.750 --> 13:06.870
Are you hungry?

13:43.690 --> 13:44.560
This...

13:45.420 --> 13:46.220
Your Majesty.

13:48.600 --> 13:49.560
What are you doing?

13:49.560 --> 13:50.350
Princess Fu!

13:50.370 --> 13:54.030
Do you know that holding the Empress hostage
is a crime of treason?

13:55.200 --> 13:56.400
Step back, all of you!

13:56.500 --> 13:58.100
This is a crime of treason!

13:58.100 --> 13:59.230
Raising assassins,

13:59.380 --> 14:00.620
attempting to assassinate His Majesty,

14:00.620 --> 14:02.010
and framing the Crown Prince

14:02.010 --> 14:03.540
are also crimes of treason.

14:04.170 --> 14:04.770
Move!

14:06.980 --> 14:07.500
This...

14:15.460 --> 14:16.650
Everyone, step back!

14:16.650 --> 14:17.250
Step back!

14:19.410 --> 14:20.290
Zhan Ziyu,

14:20.860 --> 14:22.010
tell everyone here,

14:22.310 --> 14:23.170
who ordered you

14:23.650 --> 14:26.010
to use assassins to kill His Majesty

14:26.300 --> 14:27.690
and frame the Crown Prince?

14:27.690 --> 14:28.750
And who ordered you

14:28.890 --> 14:30.980
to eliminate the Crown Prince

14:31.290 --> 14:33.140
on his way to Youzhou?

14:33.340 --> 14:33.930
Speak!

14:39.410 --> 14:40.290
Zhan Ziyu,

14:41.090 --> 14:43.220
I don't understand what she's saying.

14:43.620 --> 14:47.260
Can you explain it to me?

14:49.140 --> 14:50.410
Do you remember

14:51.090 --> 14:52.690
the scene when you brought me back

14:52.690 --> 14:54.580
from the destroyed village in Nanxi

14:54.580 --> 14:55.890
15 years ago?

14:55.890 --> 14:56.620
Nanxi?

14:57.290 --> 14:58.690
Zhan Ziyu is from Nanxi?

14:59.050 --> 15:00.010
Nanxi?

15:01.540 --> 15:02.730
The sky that day

15:03.450 --> 15:04.930
was as bright as today.

15:08.090 --> 15:09.660
Looking at your face,

15:10.170 --> 15:11.530
I secretly swore that

15:12.170 --> 15:15.740
I, Zhan Ziyu,

15:16.440 --> 15:18.500
would only have one woman in my heart,

15:18.840 --> 15:20.200
live only for her,

15:20.930 --> 15:23.130
and love only her for the rest of my life.

15:23.410 --> 15:24.770
That is you.

15:25.860 --> 15:26.500
It's...

15:26.500 --> 15:27.740
What a scandal!

15:27.770 --> 15:28.970
Because of this oath,

15:29.290 --> 15:30.460
I would do whatever

15:31.060 --> 15:32.260
you want me to do.

15:33.170 --> 15:34.580
As long as it's your wish,

15:35.050 --> 15:36.740
I could even give up my life,

15:37.530 --> 15:38.620
let alone bear the mere charge

15:38.620 --> 15:40.530
of assassinating His Majesty.

15:41.690 --> 15:44.930
But do you know my wish?

15:49.140 --> 15:51.140
I want to talk to Her Majesty alone.

15:55.100 --> 15:55.770
Step back!

15:56.260 --> 15:57.010
Nobody move!

16:09.070 --> 16:10.600
For the past fifteen years,

16:12.620 --> 16:15.740
I could only hide in the dark

16:19.210 --> 16:22.090
and peep at you in the corner.

16:23.570 --> 16:24.500
Your Majesty...

16:26.990 --> 16:30.350
The sunlight that day
was as warm as it is today.

16:36.050 --> 16:37.050
This...

16:42.010 --> 16:43.510
The seasons are out of order,

16:43.510 --> 16:45.250
and the universe is reversed!

16:45.500 --> 16:48.140
It's an ominous sign!

16:48.170 --> 16:49.810
What should we do?

17:29.070 --> 17:29.830
Zhen...

17:31.490 --> 17:33.890
I can no longer serve you.

17:57.680 --> 17:58.730
Are you hungry?

18:18.060 --> 18:19.490
Guards! Protect me!

18:19.800 --> 18:20.560
Don't move!

18:21.170 --> 18:22.930
Chu Qiao, a famale slave from Great Yong,

18:22.930 --> 18:25.540
conspired with a remnant
of the Nanxi Tribe, Zhan Ziyu,

18:25.540 --> 18:27.140
to frame me!

18:27.810 --> 18:29.140
Arrest them all!

18:38.100 --> 18:38.780
Stop!

18:40.490 --> 18:41.170
Minglu!

18:41.900 --> 18:44.500
They are all accomplices
of Crown Prince Li Ce!

18:44.820 --> 18:45.620
Show no mercy!

18:45.890 --> 18:47.970
Kill them,
and I will reward you handsomely!

18:47.970 --> 18:49.340
Bad news! Bad news!

18:49.340 --> 18:50.210
Something happened to His Majesty!

18:50.210 --> 18:53.730
An assassin broke into Zhengyuan Hall
and took His Majesty hostage.

18:53.730 --> 18:54.410
What...

18:54.410 --> 18:55.730
What should we do?

18:55.760 --> 18:56.670
Take them away!

19:08.780 --> 19:09.580
Your Majesty!

19:40.170 --> 19:40.970
Your Majesty!

19:45.820 --> 19:46.730
Who are you

19:47.060 --> 19:48.920
to dare hold His Majesty hostage?

19:49.030 --> 19:50.690
You don't need to know who I am.

19:51.080 --> 19:53.280
Release Princess Fu and her people now.

19:53.540 --> 19:56.070
Then, in front of all the officials,
announce

19:56.100 --> 19:59.040
that you ordered Zhan Ziyu to attempt
to assassinate His Majesty

19:59.040 --> 20:01.110
and frame Crown Prince Li Ce,

20:01.130 --> 20:02.260
and I will let him go.

20:04.620 --> 20:05.210
Empress,

20:05.690 --> 20:06.890
save me!

20:07.850 --> 20:08.970
Hurry up and release Chu Qiao
and the others,

20:08.970 --> 20:10.250
and admit that you did it.

20:10.250 --> 20:11.490
I won't believe it.

20:11.860 --> 20:13.820
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

20:13.850 --> 20:16.000
Saving His Majesty is the priority,
Your Majesty.

20:16.000 --> 20:16.630
Yes!

20:16.660 --> 20:18.520
Saving His Majesty is the priority!

20:18.520 --> 20:19.650
Audacious traitor!

20:20.060 --> 20:21.410
To frame me,

20:21.690 --> 20:25.090
you actually dare to hold His Majesty hostage
to threaten me.

20:25.300 --> 20:26.620
Who ordered you?

20:27.000 --> 20:28.600
The Crown Prince or Chu Qiao?

20:29.470 --> 20:32.070
Empress,
are you really going to save yourself

20:32.250 --> 20:34.020
at the cost of the Emperor's life?

20:34.020 --> 20:36.350
Of course I care about His Majesty's life.

20:36.620 --> 20:38.020
That is exactly why I will not negotiate

20:38.020 --> 20:39.780
with rebels and traitors.

20:40.340 --> 20:41.060
Guards!

20:41.490 --> 20:43.890
Kill the traitor
and take His Majesty back!

20:45.090 --> 20:45.890
Your Majesty!

20:46.060 --> 20:47.260
Do it now!

20:50.100 --> 20:50.900
Your Majesty!

20:53.170 --> 20:53.970
Your Majesty!

20:54.590 --> 20:55.390
Your Majesty!

21:24.470 --> 21:25.270
Your Majesty!

21:44.680 --> 21:45.420
Your Majesty!

21:45.420 --> 21:46.380
I am here!

21:46.660 --> 21:47.920
Anyone who makes a move

21:48.490 --> 21:50.290
will be punished for rebellion!

21:55.930 --> 21:56.540
Father!

22:11.560 --> 22:12.860
Your Majesty!

22:15.170 --> 22:16.670
I have come by your imperial order

22:16.670 --> 22:17.590
to protect you!

22:44.060 --> 22:44.780
Good.

22:46.120 --> 22:48.120
I have tolerated you for many years,

22:48.340 --> 22:50.070
thinking you knew your limits.

22:51.010 --> 22:54.640
I never expected that you would not only
move against the Crown Prince,

22:54.640 --> 22:56.600
but also come after me.

22:57.780 --> 22:58.860
Stop acting.

22:59.600 --> 23:03.000
You are selfish, hypocritical,
and always putting on an act.

23:04.020 --> 23:04.690
To me,

23:05.440 --> 23:07.840
to your own brother Crown Prince Maocheng,

23:08.690 --> 23:11.620
and to your people and ministers alike.

23:12.930 --> 23:14.140
You deceived me,

23:14.650 --> 23:16.020
went back on your word,

23:18.100 --> 23:19.650
and killed my child,

23:19.980 --> 23:21.710
yet still pretended to love me.

23:21.890 --> 23:22.730
For the throne,

23:22.730 --> 23:24.590
you even killed your own brother!

23:25.140 --> 23:26.730
You feign mourning him.

23:26.890 --> 23:29.020
Going out of the palace to pray for him?

23:29.330 --> 23:31.130
Your acting is so convincing...

23:32.280 --> 23:34.280
you've almost convinced yourself.

23:34.970 --> 23:36.780
If only you knew nothing

23:38.020 --> 23:39.780
and were a little more foolish.

23:40.510 --> 23:42.570
Perhaps I could continue to favor you

23:43.220 --> 23:45.220
and play this game with you forever.

23:51.980 --> 23:53.970
You shouldn't have seen through me,

23:53.970 --> 23:56.570
and you absolutely
shouldn't have exposed me.

23:56.970 --> 23:58.970
You should have kept playing along.

24:01.540 --> 24:03.170
Did it have to come to this?

24:04.730 --> 24:07.170
Is the favor I gave you not enough?

24:16.650 --> 24:18.060
Don't be afraid.

24:18.840 --> 24:20.490
I never intended to kill you.

24:21.140 --> 24:23.730
Because I never wanted to die with you.

24:24.760 --> 24:25.490
In this life,

24:26.170 --> 24:28.410
in heaven or in hell,

24:29.110 --> 24:30.720
I never want to see you again.

24:33.460 --> 24:34.650
This world—

24:39.950 --> 24:41.180
I don't want it.

24:43.730 --> 24:44.660
Your Majesty...

24:58.910 --> 25:00.040
Your Majesty!

25:28.450 --> 25:29.020
Ce!

26:11.110 --> 26:11.720
Zhen.

26:22.330 --> 26:24.330
The sunshine is so beautiful today.

27:07.650 --> 27:08.220
How is he?

27:08.250 --> 27:10.060
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

27:10.060 --> 27:11.890
His Majesty has a pre-existing condition.

27:11.890 --> 27:13.700
Coupled with years of excess
and lack of restraint,

27:13.700 --> 27:15.190
he was already critically ill.

27:15.190 --> 27:16.190
This incident

27:16.380 --> 27:18.170
has completely drained his vitality.

27:18.170 --> 27:18.970
I'm afraid...

27:19.210 --> 27:21.270
I'm afraid there will be no recovery.

27:28.020 --> 27:28.880
Your Highness,

27:29.020 --> 27:31.350
His Majesty has been unwell for many days,

27:31.370 --> 27:33.610
but a nation cannot be without a ruler
even for a single day.

27:33.610 --> 27:35.930
Please make preparations

27:36.180 --> 27:37.420
in advance.

27:44.240 --> 27:47.240
Please make preparations in advance,
Your Highness.

28:10.340 --> 28:11.100
Mother,

28:12.830 --> 28:14.320
Father is very ill.

28:15.500 --> 28:16.690
After what you did,

28:18.100 --> 28:20.230
he likely does not have many days left.

28:20.540 --> 28:22.670
I know you don't want to be with Father,

28:23.620 --> 28:25.280
so I overruled all objections

28:25.880 --> 28:27.740
and insisted on burying you here.

28:28.490 --> 28:30.100
You will not see him again.

28:31.200 --> 28:33.330
I know you do not want me to come see you,

28:33.850 --> 28:35.540
but I did not come empty-handed.

28:35.540 --> 28:37.870
I brought your favorite green rice balls.

28:51.210 --> 28:52.170
Mother!

28:53.820 --> 28:54.620
Mother!

28:58.410 --> 28:59.060
Mother,

28:59.590 --> 29:02.040
do you like the flower I picked for you?

29:03.170 --> 29:04.500
I'll put it in your hair.

29:17.970 --> 29:18.650
Mother,

29:19.100 --> 29:20.410
if you don't like it,

29:21.580 --> 29:23.890
I won't do it again.

29:28.040 --> 29:28.630
Ce.

29:43.580 --> 29:45.910
These are your favorite green rice balls.

29:48.650 --> 29:49.890
I know you

29:50.300 --> 29:51.620
had never loved me.

29:52.570 --> 29:54.490
And I know you despised me.

29:54.880 --> 29:56.680
You didn't even want to touch me.

29:57.890 --> 29:58.690
I even know that you

29:58.690 --> 30:00.890
wanted to cut me into a thousand pieces.

30:02.250 --> 30:04.530
But in the dead of night,

30:05.300 --> 30:07.700
I still fantasize
about lying in your arms,

30:07.970 --> 30:09.650
listening to your stories.

30:10.780 --> 30:12.040
Fantasizing about...

30:13.340 --> 30:15.060
falling asleep

30:16.450 --> 30:17.650
to your lullabies

30:19.690 --> 30:21.150
and never waking up again.

30:30.890 --> 30:33.500
His Majesty has arrived!

30:56.800 --> 30:59.690
Li Yan, the legitimate son
of the late Prince of Chang, Heir Luo,

30:59.690 --> 31:00.970
has inherited generations
of loyalty and bravery

31:00.970 --> 31:02.730
and is both virtuous and capable.

31:02.730 --> 31:04.930
He is hereby enfeoffed as Prince of Luo.

31:04.970 --> 31:06.380
He is granted a python robe,

31:06.380 --> 31:09.420
1,000 qing of estate land, 300 houses,

31:09.450 --> 31:13.160
500 bolts of fine silk,
and 100 fine horses.

31:14.100 --> 31:16.170
Thank you, Your Majesty.

31:27.360 --> 31:28.160
Prince of Luo.

31:34.950 --> 31:35.660
Leave us.

31:38.850 --> 31:41.640
Truly, one cannot judge by appearance.
You have hidden your strength well.

31:41.640 --> 31:44.640
I did not expect you
to be so calculating and scheming.

31:46.330 --> 31:47.740
If I remember correctly,

31:48.250 --> 31:49.140
the palace prayer ceremony
on the 15th of each month

31:49.140 --> 31:51.480
is handled by the Ministry of Rites.

31:51.620 --> 31:53.170
If it were not for you, Minister of Rites,

31:53.170 --> 31:54.490
making things convenient for Chu Qiao,

31:54.490 --> 31:55.450
how could she have appeared

31:55.450 --> 31:56.850
in Youtian Hall that day?

32:10.930 --> 32:12.730
So you betrayed your allegiance

32:12.980 --> 32:14.180
just for a stupid robe

32:15.020 --> 32:16.350
and a few shabby houses?

32:31.100 --> 32:34.100
Prince of Luo, wearing this python robe
that brings you honor,

32:34.100 --> 32:35.790
you really do look every bit the refined

32:35.790 --> 32:37.750
and upright gentleman.

32:46.690 --> 32:47.340
Chunxing!

32:47.580 --> 32:48.540
Pack my things!

32:48.540 --> 32:49.760
I'm going back to Great Yong.

32:49.760 --> 32:50.350
Chun'er!

32:55.300 --> 32:56.410
Why aren't you packing?

32:56.410 --> 32:58.350
Your Highness,
please don't speak in anger.

32:58.350 --> 32:59.540
Now that His Highness has been enfeoffed,

32:59.540 --> 33:00.960
you will be a princess consort.

33:00.960 --> 33:01.820
In all of Biantang,

33:01.820 --> 33:03.220
no one will dare bully...

33:06.270 --> 33:06.930
Let go of me!

33:07.490 --> 33:08.810
You're hurting me!

33:19.570 --> 33:21.700
You're acting tough in front of me now,

33:21.870 --> 33:22.890
but in front of Chu Qiao and Li Ce,

33:22.890 --> 33:24.090
you're just a coward!

33:24.410 --> 33:25.810
I can't stand it anymore.

33:25.920 --> 33:28.380
I'm going back to Great Yong
to find Zhao Che!

33:29.430 --> 33:30.410
Let go! Let go of me!

33:30.410 --> 33:31.690
Zhao Chun'er, enough!

33:31.690 --> 33:32.730
Let me go!

33:33.210 --> 33:34.210
Don't be naive!

33:34.580 --> 33:35.580
Do you think your Zhao Che

33:35.580 --> 33:36.710
will still want you?

33:37.170 --> 33:38.610
We've been married for days.

33:38.610 --> 33:40.740
Has he ever sent anyone to check on you?

33:41.130 --> 33:42.410
Your title as Princess

33:42.730 --> 33:43.780
is just a toy he gave you

33:43.780 --> 33:45.730
to placate a child.

33:47.490 --> 33:48.340
Let go!

33:49.690 --> 33:50.970
Listen to me!

33:51.620 --> 33:53.450
You're not allowed to go anywhere!

33:53.450 --> 33:54.970
Just stay in the mansion.

33:57.780 --> 33:59.620
You, a deposed princess,

34:00.100 --> 34:02.170
and I, a useless prince,

34:02.690 --> 34:04.540
are a match made in heaven.

34:05.330 --> 34:08.090
I will achieve every single thing

34:08.850 --> 34:10.170
I promised you!

34:16.540 --> 34:17.540
Keep an eye on her.

34:17.850 --> 34:19.810
Don't let her leave this room.

34:20.500 --> 34:21.100
Yes.

35:01.730 --> 35:03.460
I thought you were smart.

35:04.330 --> 35:06.690
I didn't expect you to be so stupid too.

35:07.060 --> 35:08.900
Don't stop me! Let me die!

35:08.900 --> 35:11.730
Let go of me! Let go of me!

35:17.250 --> 35:18.450
Why do you want to die?

35:18.730 --> 35:19.930
Is it for the Empress,

35:20.060 --> 35:21.290
or Zhan Ziyu?

35:23.420 --> 35:24.020
I...

35:33.690 --> 35:35.460
After the Nanxi Tribe was wiped out,

35:35.460 --> 35:37.200
you were separated from Zhan Ziyu

35:37.200 --> 35:38.460
and sold into slavery.

35:39.330 --> 35:40.930
It took him years to find you.

35:41.690 --> 35:42.690
You were a slave.

35:43.000 --> 35:44.190
You should know

35:44.620 --> 35:45.770
the life you're living now

35:45.770 --> 35:47.770
is thousands of times better than before.

35:47.770 --> 35:49.500
You survived back then.

35:50.140 --> 35:51.400
But now you want to die?

35:51.770 --> 35:53.060
Isn't that too stupid?

35:53.650 --> 35:55.850
Ziyu is my only family

35:55.850 --> 35:56.970
in this world.

35:57.180 --> 35:59.620
My clansmen were killed by the Empress.

35:59.720 --> 36:02.120
Even my only family is dead.

36:04.420 --> 36:06.530
What's the point of living?

36:18.290 --> 36:19.580
The child in your womb

36:19.790 --> 36:21.310
is your only family.

36:21.850 --> 36:23.020
The child?

36:23.460 --> 36:25.420
Although Zhan Ziyu is your brother,

36:25.420 --> 36:26.900
he exploited your youth

36:27.450 --> 36:28.780
to work for the Empress.

36:33.360 --> 36:34.440
You are so smart.

36:34.940 --> 36:36.370
And Li Ce is a kind

36:36.520 --> 36:37.780
and affectionate man.

36:38.470 --> 36:40.330
Now he is the Emperor of Biantang,

36:41.020 --> 36:43.900
and you are carrying his only child.

36:45.820 --> 36:47.280
Think about it carefully.

37:28.100 --> 37:28.980
These two swords

37:28.980 --> 37:30.090
represent

37:30.120 --> 37:31.980
that we will be together forever.

37:32.190 --> 37:33.360
What my mother lost,

37:33.770 --> 37:35.690
I'll win back for her.

37:35.720 --> 37:36.980
Kill this witch!

37:36.980 --> 37:38.800
If we offer her to the King of Great Yan,

37:38.800 --> 37:40.070
we'll be saved.

37:40.370 --> 37:41.250
Catch her!

37:41.250 --> 37:42.500
Set off!

37:43.210 --> 37:44.620
Long live Great Yan!

37:44.650 --> 37:46.170
Crush Biantang!
